comments: Simons (POR) is moving alongside Durant's (BKN) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together at the end of the drive.
Harris (BKN) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact that occurs during Winslow's (POR) layup attempt.
O'Neale (BKN) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Lillard (POR) establishes his left foot as his pivot and maintains it as he starts his dribble.
Hart (POR) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Hart (POR) turns as he passes the ball and the contact with Watanabe (BKN) is marginal.
Winslow (POR) rests an arm on Simmons' (BKN) arm as the two players pursue the rebound but the contact is marginal.
Winslow (POR) reaches in and initiates marginal body contact with O'Neale (BKN) as he attempts to pass.
Winslow (POR) is moving alongside Durant's (BKN) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Durant (BKN) delivers contact to Winslow (POR) that dislodges him from his legally obtained defensive position.
Simmons (BKN) initiates contact to Nurkic's (POR) head as both players pursue the rebound.
Durant (BKN) establishes the ball in the frontcourt within eight seconds.
Winslow (POR) initiates contact with Durant's (BKN) arm that affects his SQBR.
Durant (BKN) initiates body contact with Nurkic (POR) that affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Grant (POR) legally contests Durant's (BKN) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
As Simons (POR) reaches for the rebound, incidental contact occurs with O'Neale's (BKN) arm that does not affect his putback shot attempt.

After communicating with the Replay Center, it is determined that there was 0.1 seconds remaining on the game clock when the ball goes out of bounds. The game clock is reset to 00:00.1 and resumed from the point of interruption.
